<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3be43dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0999139b4eb2b446c77a3a947326f1e2057f1571","tid":485333,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"97後個班全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後生既真&middot;香港人已經20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddf7cdfd8a4a5460904a2d28d4c66b5994f26de","tid":485333,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"BN(O) passport holders can join the British Army and get British Citizenship after five years' service - <br />\n<br />\n英倫追夢 誕首名港產御林軍樂手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170813/00176_045.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170813%2F00176_045.html&d=tM%2Bj00NxWG6U68T3aQiASwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=138b5d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170813/00176_045.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">David憶述，源於幾年前一次聚餐時偶遇英國陸軍音樂總監，對方提起英國御林軍樂隊招募新隊員，他持有英國國民海外護照（BNO）身份也可參與招聘考試，故決定一試。</span>軍樂隊考試分兩部分，體能為先，音樂第二。對於當年三十三歲的他來說，體能測試是極大的挑戰，首輪面試便因跑步不達標而失敗。但他並沒有放棄，返港苦操三、四個月後，二○一三年通過所有測試，成功取錄。<br />\n<br />\n要成為正式御林軍，需接受長達半年基本訓練及音樂訓練，全天候廿四小時入住軍營及絕對服從命令。而David隸屬陸軍部隊軍樂隊Band of the Grenadier Guards，日常工作主要為白金漢宮每兩日一次換兵儀式伴奏，帶領新兵接替舊兵當值；軍樂隊亦在大型歡迎儀式演奏歡迎國家元首，他曾有幸接待國家主席習近平，又曾參與英女王壽辰的閱兵儀式等。他憑於軍隊的優秀表現及領導才能，入伍兩年後，即從單簧管樂手升為首席單簧管樂手。<span style=\"color: red;\">他現長居英國，還有一年可入籍</span>，目標是繼續在軍隊攀升，成為終身職業。"},{"pid":"253879cf4911e42c02804393dfcb474e9033fd95","tid":485333,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"咩事攪分化 ?  5 毛手法 ?<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 有 BNO"},{"pid":"8deec5e0188dbcf51e35339f856cbcde27d7642a","tid":485333,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事攪分化 ?  5 毛手法 ?<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 有 BNO</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3229f6fd46936bfe3e668778d1f67fd1860edfed","tid":485333,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>97後個班全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後生既真&middot;香港人已經20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6f11357f2b5038a1adbb3d7cda0741118d7343","tid":485333,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實揸特區護照咪一樣冇中國居留權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一樣有 你有無聽過你番大陸有限期？<br />\n唯一分別你無戶籍係大陸姐"},{"pid":"832a058590ed4aa6d66d046f1e882bfae904af30","tid":485333,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實揸特區護照咪一樣冇中國居留權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一樣有 你有無聽過你番大陸有限期？<br />\n唯一分別你無戶籍係大陸姐</blockquote><br />\n唔好用入境權偷換居留權<br />\n而且個入境權仲要申請先有，仲有佢可以唔批"},{"pid":"4d49801bdd7a3adaf189d4b1317dc3d8224be708","tid":485333,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T13:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>祝眾五毛多重癌症長期彌留</strong></span>"},{"pid":"21602030830e1659c85b836